          Fun for all ages, the Midway offers exciting rides, classic games, and
          a variety of food vendors. From thrilling rides to nostalgic games and
          tasty treats, there's something for everyone to enjoy.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-8 text-center">
          <div
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-blue-50 px-4 py-2"
          >
            <Ticket className="h-4 w-4 text-blue-600" />
            <span class="text-sm text-blue-800">
              Pay One Price wristbands include unlimited rides during
              specified hours
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>
        {/* Midway schedule */}
        <div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
          {
            rideBandSchedule.map((day, index) => (
              <Card className="hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300 bg-black/80">
                <CardHeader className="pb-4">
                  <CardTitle className="flex items-center gap-2 text-lg text-white">
                    <Calendar className="h-5 w-5 text-blue-500" />
                    {day.date}
                  </CardTitle>
                </CardHeader>

                <CardContent className="space-y-6 pb-6">
                  <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                    <Clock className="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" />
                    <div>
                      <p class="font-medium text-neutral-300">Midway Hours</p>
                      <p class="text-neutral-100">{day.midwayHours}</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>

                  <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                    <DollarSign className="h-5 w-5 text-emerald-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" />
                    <div>
                      <p class="font-medium text-white">Wristband Cost</p>
                      <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-emerald-500">
                        {day.wristbandCost}
                      </p>
                    </div>
                  </div>

                  <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                    <Ticket className="h-5 w-5 text-purple-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" />
                    <div>
                      <p class="font-medium text-white">Pay One Price Hours</p>
                      <p class="text-neutral-300">{day.payOnePriceHours}</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </CardContent>
              </Card>
            ))
          }
        </div>
        
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* Ossi Cove Section */}
    <section id="ossi" class="pb-12 md:pb-24">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
        <h2
          class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tighter text-white sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl"
        >
          Ossi Cove
        </h2>
        <p
          class="text-muted mx-auto mt-6 max-w-5xl md:text-xl/relaxed lg:text-base/relaxed xl:text-xl/relaxed"
        >
          Named after the Choctaw word for "eagle," Ossi Cove is the place for
          family-friendly shows like the Critters Keeper Show, Dinosaur
          Experience, and Scales, Tails & Teeth. It’s a place for wild fun and
          learning.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-12 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
          {
            ossiCove.map((event) => (
              <Card className="mt-12 overflow-hidden border-none bg-black/70 p-0 text-white">
                <img
                  src={`/family/${event.image}.jpg`}
                  alt={event.title}
                  class="aspect-square w-full object-cover"
                />
                <div class="p-6 text-center">
                  <h3 class="mb-2 mt-[-20px] text-xl font-semibold md:text-2xl">
                    {event.title}
                  </h3>
                  <p class="text-muted">{event.description}</p>
                </div>
              </Card>
            ))
          }
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* Shawi Section */}
    <section id="shawi" class="pb-12 md:pb-24">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
        <h2
          class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tighter text-white sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl"
        >
          Shawi's Discovery Zone
        </h2>
        <p
          class="text-muted mx-auto mt-6 max-w-5xl md:text-xl/relaxed lg:text-base/relaxed xl:text-xl/relaxed"
        >
          Created just for kids, Shawi’s Discovery Zone inspires learning
          through Choctaw language activities, traditional storytelling, crafts,
          and games. A fun and interactive space to connect with Choctaw
          heritage.
        </p>
        <Card
          className="mt-12 overflow-hidden border-none bg-black/70 p-4 text-white"
        >
          <h2
            class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tighter text-white sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl"
          >
            Schedule Coming Soon!
          </h2>
